reviews.review_text: Happy to finally hear Thanx to all involved.  All songs are slightly cut, second set is incomplete and the sound is less than desirable.  Still the band is raunchy and if you like Pig rapping down, Good Lovin' will be a treat.  1st set features the only electric Oh Boy and Hog For You Baby is the only one since 1966.  I have only heard the middle night of this run and glad to finally get this one.  Peace
